A cyberpunk cityscape at night where streams of glowing data packets flow through neon-lit corridors between towering server monoliths. In the foreground, a translucent shield barrier pulses with electric blue energy, deflecting red hostile particles that scatter and dissolve on impact. The rejected particles leave trails that feed into monitoring screens embedded in nearby structures, displaying abstract waveform patterns. The scene has deep purple shadows, cyan and magenta accent lighting, rain-slicked surfaces reflecting the glow, and a moody atmospheric haze. Camera angle is slightly low, looking up at the protective barrier as it actively repels threats while logging each attempt.
